      "acceptanceCriteria": "Boundary conditions applied in simulation must be demonstrated equivalent to those measured experimentally; inlet velocity profiles and outlet pressure conditions require experimental characterization.",
      "rationale": "Inlet boundary conditions assumed uniform velocity profile; experimental setup used tubing inlet with developing flow not characterized. Equivalency between simulation and experimental boundary conditions not formally established. Achieved level 1 against required level 4."
